rows.label: qst202016_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, from Daddy? Well, thanks for this.
Must've been quite a trek.

rows.label: qst202016_msg0011
rows.name:
Golden bracers... I remember hearing
about these when I was a kid.

rows.label: qst202016_msg0003
rows.name:
Daddy and Musubi are still their same old
selves, I take it? I haven't seen them
for yonks.

rows.label: qst202016_msg0004
rows.name:
Don't tell me - Musubi is still making
her same old dumplings?

rows.label: qst202016_msg0005
rows.name: Me and my sister used to love those.

rows.label: qst202016_msg0006
rows.name:
We ought to all get together again
sometime. I'd love to see Musubi again.

rows.label: qst202016_msg0008
rows.name:
Could you pass this onto Daddy
for me? It's an accessory. I made it
myself.

rows.label: qst202016_msg0009
rows.name:
He'll probably never use it, but at
least it'll remind him how we are.

rows.label: qst202016_msg101
rows.name:
Musubi is the only mother we ever really
knew. She was always there for us.

rows.label: qst202016_msg102
rows.name: She's such an important person to us.

rows.label: qst202016_msg103
rows.name:
I can almost taste her dumplings now.
Mmmm...
